Output daemon.gif

Set Shell "zsh"
Set FontSize 18
Set Width 1200
Set Height 720
Set Padding 20
Set WindowBar Colorful
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 50ms
Set PlaybackSpeed 1.3

Type "veles tui" Enter
Sleep 4s
Type "/daemon" Enter
Sleep 4s
Down
Sleep 1s
Down
Sleep 1s
Sleep 2s
Escape
Sleep 1.5s
Ctrl+D
Sleep 1s
